	JL Dance Company is thrilled to share with you all TWO amazing nights of talent, passion and dance! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The dancers have worked tirelessly to bring you diverse performances featuring styles from ballet to hip-hop. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All levels. All ages. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join JL Dance Co. for a family fun show that is full of energy and excitement. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Two nights. Two completely different shows.<span><br/></span><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\">Let's Go 2026</span> IS:</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Thu June 18: \"LAGOM\" Showcase<span><br/></span>Fri June 19: \"INDELIBLE\" Showcase</span>
""";
