<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/189602AGPCSTLRPSMCVSGDDKGLNGSJPDG> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "VIREO Dance - Thrive XI";
  schema:description """
	VIREO School of Performing Arts Ltd proudly presents <span class=\"BoldText\">Thrive XI</span> — a vibrant celebration of VIREO’s 11th season of dance. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join VIREO Dance for an unforgettable weekend showcasing the talent, dedication, and passion of VIREO’s dancers. With three unique performance lineups, Thrive XI features an exciting mix of Ballet, Jazz, Tap, Contemporary, Hip Hop, Lyrical, Acro, Musical Theatre, and more. Each showcase offers a different lineup, so you are encouraged you to experience more than one performance! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From the youngest performers to the award-winning Company teams, every show is packed with energy, artistry, and heart—an experience you won’t want to miss. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets go on sale Friday, May 15 @ 12pm! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Showcase A — June 11 at 7:00 PM <span><br/></span>Showcase B — June 12 at 7:00 PM <span><br/></span>Showcase C — June 13 at 7:00 PM</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Photo by John Bonner Photography
""";
